ive","typical":"~15-25 min","notes":"Direct A31 access westbound"},{"to":"London Waterloo","mode":"Rail (from Winchester/Alton)","typical":"~1h to 1h15 + station access","notes":"Use Winchester or Alton stations depending on preference"}]},"prices":{"summary":"SO24 values are influenced by Alresford demand and South Downs proximity, with family houses and period homes often priced above county averages.","asOf":"2026-05","sourceUrl":"https://www.rightmove.co.uk/house-prices/SO24.html"},"thingsToDo":["Walk/cycle routes toward the South Downs and Itchen Valley","Alresford town centre, shops and watercress-line attractions nearby"],"placesToEat":["The Ship Inn / local pubs in Bishop’s Sutton-Alresford area","Cafés and restaurants in New Alresford"],"pros":["Excellent access to Alresford while retaining village setting","Strong road link to Winchester via A31"],"cons":["A31 proximity can affect noise for some properties","Rail requires drive/bus to a station"],"whoItSuits":"Good for families and professionals who want village-scale living with quick access to Alresford schools/services and straightforward commuting links to Winchester and London routes.","broadbandMedianMbps":null,"nearestStation":null,"primarySupermarket":null,"images":[],"sources":[{"label":"Wikipedia — Bishop’s Sutton","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bishop%27s_Sutton"},{"label":"Bishop’s Sutton Primary School","url":"https://www.bishopssutton.hants.sch.uk/"},{"label":"Rightmove House Prices SO24","url":"https://www.rightmove.co.uk/house-prices/SO24.html"},{"label":"National Rail — Winchester station","url":"https://www.nationalrail.co.uk/stations/winchester/"}]},{"id":"bishop-s-waltham-so32","name":"Bishop''s Waltham","village":"Bishop''s Waltham","town":"Southampton","county":"Hampshire","postcode":"SO32","hubCity":"Southampton","regionDir":"North","settlementType":"Non-City","subRegion":"Southampton","coords":{"lat":50.94192,"lng":-1.21376},"coordsSource":"postcode-outward-approx","houseTypeI